"Ukuze usebenzise izinhlelo zokusebenza noma idatha ekule drayivu, ixhume kabusha. Ngokunye, ungakwazi ukukhetha ukukhohlwa lesi sitoreji uma idrayivu ingatholakali.

Uma ukhetha ukukhohlwa, yonke idatha equkethwe idrayivu izolahleka unaphakade.

Ungaka kabusha izinhlelo zokusebenza emuva kwesikhathi, kodwa idatha elondolozwe kule drayivu izolahleka."

"Lokhu kudinga ukuthi idrayivu ye-USB ifomethwe ukuze yenziwe ivikeleke. Ngemuva kokufometha ngokuphephile, le drayivu izosebenza kuphela ngale divayisi. Ukufometha kususa yonke idatha okwamanje egcinwe kudrayivu. Ukuze ugweme ukulahlekelwa yidatha, cabanga ngokwenza isipele."
"Ngemuva kokufometha, ungasebenzisa le drayivu ye-USB kwamanye amadivayisi. Yonke idatha izosulwa. Cabanga ngokwenza isipele kuqala ngokuhambisa izinhlelo zokusebenza kwesinye isitoreji sedivayisi."
"Hambisa izithombe zakho, amafayela nedatha yohlelo lokusebenza ku-%1$s. Lokhu kungathatha amaminithi ambalwa. Ezinye izinhlelo zokusebenza ngeke zisebenze ngokulungile ngesikhathi sokuhanjiswa."
"Lokhu kungathatha isikhathi. Sicela ungasusi idrayivu.\nEzinye izinhlelo zokusebenza ngeke zisebenze ngokulungile ngesikhathi sokuhanjiswa."

"Ungaqhubeka, kodwa izinhlelo zokusebenza eziyiswe kule ndawo singahle zingasheshi futhi ukudluliswa kwedatha kungathatha isikhathi eside. Naka ukusebenzisa idrayivu esheshayo ngokusebenza okungcono."
"Izinhlelo zokusebenza kulesi sitoreji sale divayisi zizomisa ukusebenza uma ikhishwa. Le drayivu ye-USB ifomethwe ukuze isebenze kule divayisi kuphela. Ngeke ize isebenze kunoma yimaphi amanye"
"Ungasusi idrayivu ngesikhathi sokuhambisa.\nUhlelo lokusebenza lwe-%1$s kule divayisi ngeke luze lutholakale kuze kuqedwe ukuhambisa."
"Yonke idatha yakho elondolozwe kule drayivu izolahleka unaphakade ngokuthi \'Khohlwa\'. Ungathanda ukuqhubeka?"

"Ngemva kokufaka iphinikhodi, ukusetha kungathatha amaminithi angafika ku-2 ukuqeda"

"I-Google isebenzisa lesi sici emikhiqizweni njenge-Google Now ne-Google Amamephu. Ukuvula ukubikwa kwendawo kuvumela noma yimuphi umkhiqizo we-Google esebenzisa lesi sici igcina futhi isebenzise idatha yakho yendawo yakamuva yedivayisi ngokuxhumana ne-Akhawunti yakho ye-Google."

"Uma umlando wedawo uvuliwe kule akhawunti, i-Google ingagcina idatha yakho yendawo yedivayisi ukuze usetshenziswe izinhlelo zakho zokusebenza.

Isibonelo, i-Google Amamephu ikunika izinkombhandlela, futhi i-Google Now ingakwazisa mayelana nethrafikhi yokuhamba.

Ungavala umlando wendawo noma kunini, kodwa ukwenza kanjalo akuyisusi. Ukuze ubuke futhi uphathe umlando wendawo yakho, vakashela ku-maps.google.com/locationhistory."

"Lokhu kuzosusa wonke umlando wendawo obekwe kusuka kule divayisi yale-akhawunti ye-Google. Awukwazi ukuhlehlisa lokhu kususwa. Ezinye izinhlelo zokusebenza, okufaka phakathi i-Google Now, kuzomisa ukusebenza."
